exif: {"Image ImageDescription": "Filipino street children hang on to a passenger jeep as they roam the streets of Manila, 24 September 2007.     Child neglect and abuse is a growing social problem in the country where 40 percent of 80 million Filipinos live under the poverty. The 7th Asian Regional Conference of the International Society for the Prevention of Child Abuse and Neglect has opened a three-day meeting in the Philippine capital sponsored by UNICEF.
